### Cross-Instance Test
### This verifies data isolation: cache1 has Alice, cache2 has Bob
### GET - Verify cache1 still has Alice
GET {{baseUrl}}/services/caching/api/cache1/get/user-profile-1
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

